Privacy Policy for My Pet


Welcome to My Pet! This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and handle user data. It is important to us that you understand the information we collect and how we use it.

1. Information We Collect:

We collect the following registration information:

	User-provided information during the registration process, including but not limited to name, email address, and any additional information voluntarily provided.

2. How We Collect Information:

We collect registration information when:

	Users voluntarily provide information during the registration process.

3. How We Use Information:

We use the collected information for the following purposes:

	To create and manage user accounts so users can buy their pet products.

4. Data Sharing:

	We do not share personal or sensitive user data with any third parties, including third-party service providers, advertisers, etc.

5. Data Security:

	We employ secure data handling procedures to protect personal and sensitive user data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.

6. Data Retention and Deletion:
	
	DATA DELETION POLICY

	Purpose
	
	This document sets out our policy for responding to requests for deletion of data. This document explains the rights of the data subject in relation to data deletion and the 	responsibilities of My Pet Co., Ltd in responding with such a request.

	Individual Rights
	
	An individual has the right to erasure, also known as the right to be forgotten. The principle underpinning this right is to enable an individual to request the deletion or removal 	of personal data where there is no compelling reason for its continued processing.

	
	Data Deletion Request
	
	Our Service may give you the ability to delete certain information about you from within the Service. You may update, amend, or delete your information at any time by signing in to 	your Account, if you have one, and visiting the account settings section that allows you to manage your personal information.

	
	You can request to delete your data from our systems by the following steps:

	Sign in to your Account...
	Click My Profile, and navigate to Delete Account.
	In the Delete Account section, click the reason why you want to delete.
	And then, click Delete My Account.
	
	If you wish to have your personal information deleted from our systems, you can submit a data deletion request by contacting us at care@My Pet.com or through our data deletion 	request form.
	
	How can data be deleted?
	
	A user of My Pet, can delete the user account upon request (via email to wailinn@mypetmm.com). This data is deleted from the system immediately and cannot be recovered by any 	users or My Pet employees after this point. Data which has been deleted or otherwise destroyed cannot be recovered at any time. Sufficient warning is given to the account 	administrator before data are permanently deleted. Data may still remain in the systems back-up files, which will be deleted periodically.

	Data Deletion Timeline
	Information may be deleted from our eCommerce upon request to wailinn@mypetmm.com. We undertake to perform the deletion within one month (30 calendar days) and will send you a 	confirmation once the information has been deleted. Wherever possible, we will aim to complete the request in advance of the deadline.

	What information does My Pet retain?
	My Pet stores data about individuals in order to create a recycling report. We store name, e-mail and subsequent recycling item for each individual in order to create a report, 	which is stored on our secure servers in Myanmar. These data are stored and used in accordance with our Privacy Policy, which can be found at: https://My Pet.com/privacypolicy/. 	If consent is provided, personal data (including the above, plus address, telephone number and notes) may be stored in our eCommerce system for the purposes of contacting you 	regarding My Pet news, products and promotions.

7. Contact Information:

If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding your privacy, you can contact us at:

By email: care@shopdoora.com,wailinn@mypetmm.com

