9. Non-Editable and Readable:

This privacy policy is non-editable and readable in a standard browser without any plug-ins or special handlers (no PDFs).

10. Entity Reference:

This privacy policy refers to the entity named in the app's Google Play listing as My Pet.

By using My Pet, you agree to the terms outlined in this privacy policy. We may update this policy periodically, so please review it regularly. Your continued use of the app after any changes to this policy constitutes your acceptance of those changes.

